videos.description: Qadree Ollison breaks through the middle for a six-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Ollison punches it in for Pitt's first touchdown

videos.description: Qadree Ollison rushes for a five-yard touchdown for his second score of the game.
videos.headline: Ollison scores 2nd TD of game

videos.description: A.J. Davis plows through two defenders for a one-yard touchdown in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Davis pushes through defenders for TD

videos.description: Hunter Wells finds Christian Turner for a 25-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Turner's TD cuts Youngstown State's deficit

videos.description: Hunter Wells finds  Christian Turner for a 43-yard touchdown to tie the game.
videos.headline: Turner's 2nd TD of the 4th quarter ties the game

videos.description: Robert Lee and Dustin Fox discuss the top plays from  Pittsburgh's 28-21 victory over Youngstown State.
videos.headline: Pittsburgh holds on to beat Youngstown State
